  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Get a server today and play with your friends! Click <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\">HERE</a> or below banner &amp; Use Code <strong>GAMERPOTION</strong> to get 25 off!</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/684/717/cbf4e971-7207-4602-bd76-b44081f9b7df.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Origins Mod-Required-black?style=plastic\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Server Side-Supported-green?style=plastic\" /> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/gamerpotion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/buy me a coffee-support-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/uCPfPBvsRJ\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/870825743788158986?color=blue&amp;style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/GamerPotionDev\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/my other-projects-orange?style=plastic\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/get%20a%20server-click%20here-blue?style=plastic\" /></a><br />&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>DarkOrb</h2>\n<p><br />Craft an Orb of Origin using custom recipes! |&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.gamerpotion.net/2023/07/darkorb-orb-of-origin-recipe.html\">View Changelog</a></p>\n<p><em>Server side is supported. You can install this on the server and not need to have it installed on the client.</em></p>\n<p>Created by the same authors who made <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/darkrpg\" rel=\"nofollow\">DarkRPG</a> (for a full RPG experience, get the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/darkrpg\" rel=\"nofollow\">DarkRPG modpack</a> and enjoy quests and rpg gameplay)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<p>(Your vanilla experience will be further enhanced thanks to these features)&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Allows you to craft an orb of origin using custom recipes. Each recipe caters to where your origin spawns in (overworld, nether, the end).<br /><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/origins\">Origins</a> Mod required.<br />(EMI/JEI/REI is recommended to view the recipes in game)<br /><br /></p>\n<h2>Recipes</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/700/753/orb1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"505\" height=\"247\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/700/754/orb2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"504\" height=\"249\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/700/755/orb3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"503\" height=\"245\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Permission - Feel free to use in your modpacks.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Click the banner below to get your server today! or go to <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\">BisectHosting.com</a>&nbsp; and make sure to use the code '<strong>gamerpotion</strong>' to get your 25% off.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/gamerpotion\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/608/745/bisect-banner-large3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"621\" height=\"415\" /></a></p>",
